{"tid":107353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅斯達菲：輸波唔關雲格事","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T12:43:15.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6a12217cf8bfc2ec250b48c6d2ea62ec89015b","tid":107353,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"上場1：2輸給屈福特令到阿仙奴大受打擊，不過球隊今輪比賽便要作客鬥車路士。<br />\n<br />\n雖然處境困難，不過梅斯達菲期望今場作客車仔可以帶來驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n談及上輪失手，梅斯達菲說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">球員在場上比賽，輸波應該怪責自己而非領隊。大家要檢討犯了什麼錯誤，球員要負上輸波責任。」</span><br />\n<br />\n「我們可以更早入局，因為英超比賽就是如此困難。今場大戰車路士，我們要嘗試由第一分鐘集中到最後一分秒，雖然是極之艱難，但這是反彈的好時機。」梅斯達菲認真道。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cdda673d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"ac472226e694f03636e03908700b47584fa5d263","tid":107353,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"爺爺又然"},{"pid":"9a969381d858a7cf8e23093242a997e068325123","tid":107353,"uid":10859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"輸贏唔重要 最緊要迷雲"},{"pid":"dda9e4a8412d3fe1b9bfec70f310406096d35c97","tid":107353,"uid":33712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d732a86e4a1ee20389bf1d9439082b6a8380595","tid":107353,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fbf4185e1a7714511d0041efe4a116c9cf7b37","tid":107353,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df